<sp/><sp/>*<sp/>When<sp/>not<sp/>using<sp/>hw<sp/>acceleration,<sp/>gl<sp/>will<sp/>fault<sp/>if<sp/>we<sp/>clear<sp/>the<sp/>depth<sp/>buffer<sp/>bit
